    <question>
        <prompt>What was President Andrew Johnson's background before becoming president?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Northern Republican congressman</option>
            <option letter="b">Southern Democratic senator who remained loyal to the Union</option>
            <option letter="c">Confederate general who switched sides</option>
            <option letter="d">Northern abolitionist leader</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>Andrew Johnson was a Southern Democrat from Tennessee who remained loyal to the Union during the Civil War, making him unique as the only Southern senator to retain his seat.</explanation>
